ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectCanada-Swiss Federal Council- Avoidance of Double Taxation with Respect to Taxes on Income and on Capital ** Agreement **
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to take, on behalf of Canada, the measures necessary to BRING INTO FORCE the AGREEMENT concerning the Interpretation of Article 25 of the Convention between the Government of Canada and the SWISS FEDERAL COUNCIL for the Avoidance of Double Taxation with Respect to Taxes on Income and on Capital, done at Berne on 5 May 1997, as amended by the Protocol done at Berne on 22 October 2010.
